overview.en: eCell Token作为网络主要的流通、治理、激励凭证，基于eCell 的去中心化质押委托机制，我们构筑了Consensus 节点(共识节点)体系，Consensus 节点将作为组织治理与应用推广的基石，为推动愿景的实现提供强有力的内生动能。
overview.zh: As the main circulation, governance and incentive voucher of the network, based on the decentralized pledge entrustment mechanism of ecell, we have built a consensus node system. The consensus node will be the cornerstone of organizational governance and application promotion, providing strong endogenous momentum for the realization of the vision.
